The paper deals with event-triggered control and digital communication channels, which are topics related to control systems (cs.SY), information theory (cs.IT), and robotics (cs.RO). The paper also discusses the use of encoding-decoding schemes for achieving stability, which is a topic related to machine learning (cs.LG) and neural networks (cs.NE). Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.SY, followed by cs.IT, cs.RO, cs.NE, and cs.LG.
